scene.message:
SEBEC Employee: A high{nl}
schooler in the same uniform{nl}
as you came by earlier too.{waitkey}{clearbox}For all this to happen on{nl}
your field trip day... you{nl}
kids have it rough.{waitkey}{ret}

SEBEC Employee: Who is it?!{nl}
Who rearranged the rooms{nl}
without telling me and made{nl}
a storeroom?!{waitkey}{clearbox}And stuffed weird toys{nl}
inside it, too! I won't{nl}
stand for it!!{waitkey}{ret}
